'''''Old Foreman's Treasure''''' is a [[Companion Mission]] in the chapter [[Slices of Life Before the Furnace]].

==Steps==
# Talk to Julian in the Underworld
# Go to the Great Mine to look for Hook
# Go to the clinic and ask Natasha about Fersman's condition
# Hook seems to have something to tell you. Go ask her
# Go to the Great Mine and meet up with Hook
# Talk to the suspects at the scene
# Talk to the cook to see if they're lying
# Talk to the tailor to see if they're lying
# Talk to the helper to see if they're lying
# Confront the cook and find the thief
# Confront the tailor and find the thief
# Confront the merchant and find the thief
# Confront the helper and find the thief
# Investigate the scene where the vein detector went missing
# Follow Hook and confront the suspect
# Find the packages using the information on the label
# Go to Boulder Town and consult Balaway
# Follow Hook and confront the suspect
# Return to the clinic and tell Fersman what happened

